Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}共振拒む理由なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}単純過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}I won't let you down，come along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Taking back my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}確信はその手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:13.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}I'm waiting for till the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Taking back 錆びついた意志でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:25.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Just change the world 革命に似た Calling back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:29.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fs32}Tell me what's wrong with the society that everybody is saying OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Why everybody say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Low resistance of high zest inner cells
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}rebuild the coil there is no lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}浑浑噩噩不知何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}却空有一身杀敌的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:32.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}用绝缘体般的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}拿讨厌电阻为理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}而这般拒绝共振
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}未免太过单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}为何从不放手一试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我不会让你失望 跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}找回自己前行的路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}为何从不放手一试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:08.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}坚定的信念就在手中紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:13.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}蓄势待发 只待破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:19.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}夺回所失 即便那心灵已锈迹斑斑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:25.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}用革命改写世界 正如从前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:29.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}谁来告诉我这人人称颂的世道到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Why everybody say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}热情在每一个细胞里奔流不息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}重新编织出没有谎言的未来
